### Variables (ajusta puerto si usas 8000 con docker compose)
@base = http://localhost:8080
@token = pegar_access_token_aqui

### Health (sin auth)
GET {{base}}/health

### Registro
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pepito@test.com",
  "password": "clave12345",
  "notification_preference": "email"
}

### Login — copia access_token del JSON y ponlo arriba en @token
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pepito@test.com",
  "password": "clave12345"
}

### Fondos (requiere Bearer)
GET {{base}}/funds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Perfil
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Suscribirse al fondo 3 (DEUDAPRIVADA, mínimo 50.000 COP)
POST {{base}}/funds/3/subscribe
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Misma suscripción con idempotencia (repetir = misma respuesta, sin doble cargo)
POST {{base}}/funds/3/subscribe
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: demo-subscribe-001
Idempotency-Version: 1

### Suscripciones
GET {{base}}/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Transacciones
GET {{base}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
